"iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/duhNy0EMX1igxHQN3YMuPcAokT6.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":2307,"height":1298,"file_path":"/bVN2jrxP9Al3ydPfO2JVMcaCPoV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:59:25.177+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"17살, 내 시선 끝에 서 있던 나의 첫사랑","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/TITle/81472752","overview":"보라의 둘도 없는 친구 연두는 심장 수술을 위해 미국에 가면서 자신이 좋아하는 남자 백현진에 대한 모든 정보를 수집해 달라고 보라에게 부탁한다. 보라는 백현진의 가장 친한 친구 풍운호와 먼저 친해지기로 한다. 하지만 보라의 서투른 계획은 예상치 못한 방향으로 전개된다. 새로운 세기가 오기 1년 전인 1999년, 17세가 된 보라는 첫사랑의 열병에 빠진다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":119,"tagline":"A first love pov story.","homepage":"","overview":"In 1999, a teen girl keeps close tabs on a boy in school on behalf of her deeply smitten best friend – then she gets swept up in a love story of her own."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":121,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81472752","overview":"Im Auftrag ihrer hoffnungslos verliebten Freundin, beobachtet ein Mädchen im Jugendalter heimlich einen Jungen ihrer Schule im Jahr 1999. Daraufhin wird sie allerdings selbst in ihre eigene Liebesgeschichte hineingezogen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Garota do Século 20","runtime":121,"tagline":"Um romance em terceira pessoa.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81472752","overview":"O ano é 1999 e uma adolescente começa a monitorar o garoto pelo qual a melhor amiga está apaixonada. Tudo vai bem até que um outro amor começa a dar as caras."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Una chica del siglo XX","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81472752","overview":"Yeon-du le pide a su mejor amiga Bora que recopile toda la información que pueda sobre Baek Hyun-jin mientras ella está en los Estados Unidos para someterse a una cirugía de corazón. Bora decide acercarse primero al mejor amigo de Baek, Pung Woon-ho. Sin embargo, el torpe plan de Bora se desarrolla en una dirección inesperada. En 1999, un año antes del nuevo siglo, Bora, que cumple diecisiete años, cae en la fiebre del primer amor."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":119,"tagline":"Une première histoire d'amour en pov.","homepage":"","overview":"En 1999, Bo-ra, 17 ans, s'attelle à la tâche la plus importante de son adolescence, car l'amitié est plus forte que tout, plus forte même que l'amour. Quand Yeon-doo se rend à l'étranger pour être opérée du cœur, Bo-ra promet de surveiller le premier amour de son amie et de lui raconter tous ses faits et gestes."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"20 เซนจูรี่ รักนี้ซาบซ่า","runtime":121,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ปี 1999 สาววัยทีนคอยติดตามความเคลื่อนไหวของเด็กหนุ่มในโรงเรียน ตามคำขอของเพื่อนสนิทที่ไปหลงรักเขาจนหัวปักหัวปำ จนรู้สึกหวั่นไหวกับเรื่องรักๆ ใคร่ๆ ตามไปด้วย"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"20世紀少女","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1999 年，一名青少女眼看閨密被一位男同學迷得神魂顛倒，便替她密切觀察這個男生，沒想到卻因而譜出自己的戀曲。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"دختر قرن بیستمی","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"یئوندو (نو یون‌سئو) از بهترین دوستش بورا (کیم یو‌جونگ) می‌خواهد تا تمام اطلاعاتی را که می‌تواند درباره بک هیونجین (پارک جونگ‌وو) جمع‌آوری کند، در حالی که او درجایی دیگر در ایالات متحده برای جراحی قلب است. بورا تصمیم می‌گیرد ابتدا به بهترین دوست بک، پونگ وونهو (بیون وو‌سئوک) نزدیک شود. با این حال، نقشه ناشیانه بورا در جهتی غیرمنتظره پیش می‌رود. در سال 1999، یک سال قبل از قرن جدید، بورا که هفده ساله شده است، در تب عشق اول گرفتار می‌شود."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"20世纪少女","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1999年，一名少女为了大犯花痴的好友而密切关注学校里的一个男生，结果却展开了自己的爱情故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In 1999 houdt een tiener een jongen op school nauwlettend in de gaten namens haar verliefde vriendin. Maar dan raakt ze zelf verwikkeld in een liefdesverhaal."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Holka z 20. století","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Je rok 1999. Mladá školačka slídí po informacích o klukovi, do kterého je blázen její nejlepší kamarádka – a zanedlouho se taky do někoho zamiluje až po uši."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"XX. századi lány","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Egy kedves, jószívű lány megígéri barátnőjének, hogy szemmel tartja egyik osztálytársukat, akibe a a lány titkon szerelmes. De aztán végül a saját románca ragadja magával..."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":0,"tagline":"Una storia di primo amore.","homepage":"","overview":"Yeon-du chiede alla sua migliore amica Bora di raccogliere tutte le informazioni possibili su Baek Hyun-jin mentre lei è negli Stati Uniti per un'operazione al cuore. Bora decide di avvicinarsi prima al migliore amico di Baek, Pung Woon-ho. Tuttavia, il maldestro piano di Bora prende una direzione inaspettata. Nel 1999, un anno prima del nuovo secolo, Bora, che compie diciassette anni, cade nella febbre del primo amore."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Una chica del siglo XX","runtime":0,"tagline":"Una primera historia de amor pov.","homepage":"","overview":"En 1999, una joven con un gran corazón empieza a indagar en la vida de un popular compañero de clase para hacerle un favor a su mejor amiga, que está enamorada de él."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"၂၁ ရာစုသို့ ပေးစာ","runtime":119,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://goldchannel.net/movies/20th-century-girl/","overview":"လူငယ်ပီပီ မကြာခဏစိတ်ကစားတတ်လေ့ရှိတဲ့ နှလုံးရောဂါသည်ဖြစ်သူသူငယ်ချင်းက ကြိတ်ကြိုက်ရတဲ့ကောင်လေး တစ်ယောက်တွေ့သွားလို့ အမေရိကမှာခွဲစိတ်မှုသွားခံယူဖို့မလုပ်တော့ဘဲ ပေကပ်နေတဲ့အခါ Na Bora တစ်ယောက်အ ကြံအဖန်တစ်ခုလုပ်ရပါတော့တယ်။ သူငယ်ချင်းရဲ့ crush ကလည်း တိုက်ဆိုင်ချင်တော့ သူတို့နှစ်ယောက်နဲ့တစ်ကျောင်း တည်း အတန်းတူကောင်လေးဖြစ်နေခဲ့ သူငယ်ချင်းခွဲစိတ်ရရင်ပြီးရောဆိုတဲ့ Na Bora ကတော့ ဆရာမကြီးအထာနဲ့ ၁၉၉၉ ခုနှစ်မှာတောင် Email account တွေဘာတွေ ခက်ခက်ခဲခဲကောက်ဖွင့်ပေးပြီး crush စိတ်ငယ်ထိပ်ရောက်နေတဲ့ bff ကို ကတိတစ်ခုပေးပါတော့တယ်။ အဲ့ဒီနောက်မှာတော့ အလွဲမျိုးစုံနဲ့ဘာတွေဆက်ဖြစ်မလဲဆိုတာကိုတော့"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"Το Κορίτσι του 20ού Αιώνα","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81472752","overview":"Το 1999, μια έφηβη παρακολουθεί στενά ένα αγόρι στο σχολείο για λογαριασμό της ερωτοχτυπημένης κολλητής της – ώσπου μπλέκεται σε μια δική της ερωτική ιστορία."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Девушка из 20 века","runtime":119,"tagline":"\"История первой любви от первого лица\"","homepage":"","overview":"1999 год. Начав следить за мальчиком из школы по просьбе влюбленной подруги, девочка-подросток сама находит любовь."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Дівчина XX століття","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1999 рік. Дівчинка пильно стежить за хлопцем на прохання глибоко закоханої в нього подруги, а потім потрапляє у вир власної історії кохання."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"20世紀のキミ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1999年、同じ学校の男子に恋をした親友に頼まれて、彼の行動を観察することになった女子高生。しかしそれが、思いがけないラブストーリーの始まりになる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Yeon-du, kalp ameliyatı için ABD'deyken en iyi arkadaşı Bora'dan Baek Hyun-jin hakkında toplayabildiği tüm bilgileri toplamasını ister. Bora, önce Baek'in en iyi arkadaşı Pung Woon-ho ile yakınlaşmaya karar verir. Ancak Bora'nın sakar planı beklenmedik bir yönde gelişir. 1999 yılında, yeni yüzyıldan bir yıl önce, on yedi yaşına giren Bora, ilk aşkının ateşine düşer."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En tonårstjej håller koll på skolans populäraste kille åt sin kärlekskranka bästis – men snart får hon själv upp ögonen för någon annan."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"נערה במאה ה-20","runtime":119,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"דרמת נעורים רומנטית דרום-קוריאנית.\r ב-1999, נערה עושה לחברתה המאוהבת טובה ומנהלת מעקב צמוד אחר אחד הבנים בבית הספר – עד שהיא נשאבת לסיפור אהבה משלה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"20th Century Girl","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em 1999, uma adolescente fica de olho num rapaz da escola a pedido da sua melhor amiga, que está apaixonada por ele, mas começa a viver a sua própria história de amor."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Dziewczyna z XX wieku","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jest rok 1999. 17-letnia Bo-ra (Kim Yoo-jeong) musi sprostać najważniejszemu zadaniu w jej nastoletnim życiu, w którym przyjaźń jest ważniejsza nawet od miłości. Jej przyjaciółka Yeon-doo (Roh Yoon-seo) leci za granicę na operację serca. Bo-ra ma szpiegować chłopaka, w którym Yeon-doo jest zakochana, i o wszystkim jej donosić. Aby dowiedzieć się jak najwięcej o Hyun-jinie (Park Jung-woo), Bo-ra postanawia zbliżyć się do jego przyjaciela Woon-ho (Byeon Woo-seok). Jednak nie wszystko idzie zgodnie z planem, gdy do głosu dochodzi serce Bo-ry."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Yeon-du meminta sahabatnya Bora untuk mengumpulkan semua informasi yang dia dapat tentang Baek Hyun-jin saat dia pergi ke AS untuk operasi jantung. Bora memutuskan untuk mendekati sahabat Baek, Pung Woon-ho terlebih dahulu. Namun, rencana kikuk Bora terungkap ke arah yang tidak terduga. Pada tahun 1999, setahun sebelum abad baru, Bora, yang berusia tujuh belas tahun, jatuh ke dalam demam cinta pertama."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"فتاة القرن العشرين","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81472752?preventIntent=true","overview":"في عام 1999، تراقب فتاة مراهقة عن كثب فتًى من المدرسة نيابة عن صديقتها المقرّبة والمتيّمة به إلى حدّ كبير… إلى أن تنجرف في قصّة حبّ خاصّة بها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"20 世紀少女","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1999 年，一名青少女眼看閨密被一位男同學迷得神魂顛倒，便替她密切觀察這個男生，沒想到卻因而譜出自己的戀曲。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Cô Gái Thế Kỷ 20","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Cô Gái Thế Kỷ 20 kể về năm 1999, một cô nàng tuổi teen theo dõi sát sao một nam sinh trong trường thay cho cô bạn thân si tình. Nhưng rồi, chính cô lại bị cuốn vào câu chuyện tình của riêng mình"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"فتاة القرن العشرين","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"بعد أن كلفتها صديقتها العاشقة والمرهفة المشاعر بمراقبة فتى في مدرستها الثانوية، تجد (بو را) نفسها أمام خيار صعب، بعد أن انجرفت في قصة الحب الخاصة بها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Fata secolului XX","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"În 1999, o adolescentă urmărește un băiat de la școală pentru prietena sa îndrăgostită. Însă cade la rândul ei în mrejele iubirii."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Une fille du 20e siècle","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81472752","overview":"En 1999, une adolescente suit de près un garçon de l'école pour le compte de sa meilleure amie, mais elle se trouve elle-même entraînée dans une histoire d'amour."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6571132edfe31d00c3cdaf41","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6571132edfe31d00c3cdaf41","author":"badelf","content":"This is not the most brilliant script in the world. On the other had, as rom-coms go, it was put together beautifully, and well worth watching.\r\n\r\nMy wife didn't think it was very good at the beginning - too sophomoric, I imagine. By the end, she was into it. Our problem, not being Korean, it took us near half the movie to figure out which boy was which.\r\n\r\nKim Yoo-jung is absolutely adorable, and the triumvirate of leads are all handsome.","created_at":"2023-12-07T00:34:54.984Z","updated_at":"2023-12-07T00:34:55.060Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":7,"username":"badelf","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":701561,"adult":false,"title":"Lee Chaedam's G-Spot","video":false,"overview":"An honest, open look at the sex life of erotic film actress Lee Chae-dam. She reveals her first love, her first experience, her first film, her sex lifestyle, and her love of her body.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7832,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/tnxbYOlkXbuSXZWfHYOy4l4V51h.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-26","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/y7YOnq4PxKaELAMvns0x351cpNQ.jpg","original_title":"이채담의 지스팟","original_language":"ko"},{"id":890322,"adult":false,"title":"Love Like the Falling Petals","video":false,"overview":"Haruto Asakura falls in love with hairdresser Misaki Ariake and asks her out. Watching Misaki Ariake work hard to achieve what she wants, Haruto Asakura, who almost gave up his dream to become a photographer, begins to pursue his dream again, but Misaki Ariake is diagnosed with a disease that ages her 10x faster than normal.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5669,"vote_count":99,"poster_path":"/8m2xnZAnMuydc87KCLS2gnUmidh.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-24","vote_average":7.99,"backdrop_path":"/hX9KuZQjZXrleVALumaNb6HJJ6M.jpg","original_title":"桜のような僕の恋人","original_language":"ja"},{"id":570503,"adult":false,"title":"Tune in for Love","video":false,"overview":"During the 1990s, hardworking Mi-soo and optimistic Hyun-woo meet at a bakery and fall in love while exchanging stories on a radio station, but while their paths keep crossing, the timing never seems to work out.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9558,"vote_count":316,"poster_path":"/7yaF5BOtPjQH8JDSSiVbzdrsWM4.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-28","vote_average":7.744,"backdrop_path":"/5sSCPzLhX9Ho7Llpj5N3ECjqYai.jpg","original_title":"유열의 음악앨범","original_language":"ko"},{"id":730154,"adult":false,"title":"Your Eyes Tell","video":true,"overview":"A tragic accident lead to Akari's blindness, but she clings to life and the smaller pleasures it can still afford her. She meets Rui and begins to talk to him. Rui was once a promising kickboxer, but something happened in his past. Akari's smile brings out a change in Rui. However, the two are connected in more than one way. Rui attempts to do what is right.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5089,"vote_count":502,"poster_path":"/cVn8E3Fxbi8HzYYtaSfsblYC4gl.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-23","vote_average":8.535,"backdrop_path":"/v5CEt88iDsuoMaW1Q5Msu9UZdEt.jpg","original_title":"きみの瞳が問いかけている","original_language":"ja"},{"id":962232,"adult":false,"title":"Beyond the Universe","video":false,"overview":"While waiting for a kidney transplant, a young pianist finds an unexpected connection with her doctor — and the courage to fulfill her musical dreams.","genre_ids":[10749,18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8932,"vote_count":340,"poster_path":"/AlAP6WRSBuf5cP8OgpHTF45BPUp.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-26","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/pKfvYWbxhVnGHg6By3VaxtrbLZe.jpg","original_title":"Depois do Universo","original_language":"pt"},{"id":883083,"adult":false,"title":"You Won't Be Alone","video":false,"overview":"In an isolated mountain village in 19th century Macedonia, a young feral witch accidentally kills a peasant. She assumes the peasant's shape to see what life is like in her skin, igniting a deep seated curiosity to experience life inside the bodies of others.","genre_ids":[27,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0047,"vote_count":349,"poster_path":"/qVRADANU3JpMyapKjV3eM41VlDG.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-01","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/qEYcteWFxQjfyjMrZCWcaLfHSe1.jpg","original_title":"You Won't Be Alone","original_language":"mk"},{"id":667257,"adult":false,"title":"Impossible Things","video":false,"overview":"After the death of her abusive husband, Matilde finds her new best friend in Miguel, her young, insecure, and disoriented neighbor.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2835,"vote_count":419,"poster_path":"/t2Ew8NZ8Ci2kqmoecZUNQUFDJnQ.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-17","vote_average":8.421,"backdrop_path":"/bxSBOAD8AuMHYMdW3jso9npAkgt.jpg","original_title":"Cosas imposibles","original_language":"es"},{"id":18095,"adult":false,"title":"Dragon Ball GT: A Hero's Legacy","video":false,"overview":"Son Goku Jr. is the great-great-grandson of the legendary martial artist Son Goku. However, unlike his predecessor he's not a brave fighter. He's constantly picked on by school bullies, his grandmother Pan sees this and she's worried, but even though Goku Jr. is not a strong and powerful Saiyan, he has a kind heart, and Pan loves him. When Pan gets sick Goku Jr. realizes he must do something if he doesn't want to lose Pan. Then he will remember about the legends of the Dragon Balls. It was told they granted a wish to the bearer, Goku Jr. needs a magical wish more than ever.","genre_ids":[12,28,16,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8273,"vote_count":365,"poster_path":"/reNPMjkPg9f6wgf6kHSSkKjBarL.jpg","release_date":"1997-03-26","vote_average":6.782,"backdrop_path":"/lesSOGpRuJwebgtL4vNkoRFnbil.jpg","original_title":"ドラゴンボールＧＴ 悟空外伝！ 勇気の証しは四星球","original_language":"ja"},{"id":818809,"adult":false,"title":"A Cinderella Story: Starstruck","video":false,"overview":"Finley Tremaine, a small-town farm girl, longs to spread her wings and soar as an aspiring performer. When a Hollywood film crew arrives in her sleepy town, she is determined to land a role in the production and capture the attention of handsome lead actor Jackson Stone. Unfortunately, a botched audition forces her to change course. Now, disguised as cowboy “Huck,” Finley finally gets her big break. But can she keep the charade a secret from everyone, including her evil stepmother and devious step-siblings?","genre_ids":[10749,35,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6649,"vote_count":145,"poster_path":"/vXIqSUpO84PMNt9JclXzCbPBslT.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-29","vote_average":6.879,"backdrop_path":"/1QVydsA1cMLJZP9gcKgXQDnRo