k.  Along with the Detective Boys and Ran Mouri, Conan Edogawa enters Noah's Ark to solve this mystery and ensure the perpetrator is caught.","genre_ids":[16,12,9648,878,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6027,"vote_count":224,"poster_path":"/AbgADjLIYoLAc3mayVWGBWSbjT.jpg","release_date":"2002-04-20","vote_average":7.763,"backdrop_path":"/2Gx0IssZeGhpwvULplQuf9UiI26.jpg","original_title":"名探偵コナン ベイカー街（ストリート）の亡霊","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":10220,"adult":false,"title":"Rounders","video":false,"overview":"Poker addict Mike McDermott knows the game inside out, but loses his money one night in a game to Russian-American gangster Teddy KGB. Promising his partner Jo he'll give up, he meets up with best friend Lester 'Worm' Murphy, just out of prison and owing lots of money to the wrong kind of people. McDermott becomes his co-guarantor and now there's only one way to raise the money, the pair have to get back into the game.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":3.0315,"vote_count":1871,"poster_path":"/mqbMwYGwIChnaCO55h7v8DG8Wwy.jpg","release_date":"1998-09-11","vote_average":7.009,"backdrop_path":"/tgRQsrjBKdic7llxhI7pqLJb8kS.jpg","original_title":"Rounders","original_language":"en"},{"id":10223,"adult":false,"title":"A Simple Plan","video":false,"overview":"Captivated by the lure of sudden wealth, the quiet rural lives of two brothers erupt into conflicts of greed, paranoia and distrust when over $4 million in cash is discovered at the remote site of a downed small airplane. Their simple plan to retain the money while avoiding detection opens a Pandora's box when the fear of getting caught triggers panicked behavior and leads to virulent consequences.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":2.778,"vote_count":1047,"poster_path":"/wO2gH7DMqpMeHlj5QmDhW4IkgAr.jpg","release_date":"1998-12-11","vote_average":7.206,"backdrop_path":"/gtdCmYpubVkkvTQ8rdR9tkixDSj.jpg","original_title":"A Simple Plan","original_language":"en"},{"id":10229,"adult":false,"title":"A Walk to Remember","video":false,"overview":"When the popular, restless Landon Carter is forced to participate in the school drama production, he falls in love with Jamie Sullivan, the daughter of the town's minister. Jamie has a \"to-do\" list for her life, as well as a very big secret she must keep from Landon.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":4.4325,"vote_count":4210,"poster_path":"/8lUYMvWdHA0Q0k5F76RQCeCBUkA.jpg","release_date":"2002-01-25","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/eYheokDlNmjGbG3AQAKaI0Er0Cc.jpg","original_title":"A Walk to Remember","original_language":"en"},{"id":10236,"adult":false,"title":"The Way We Were","video":false,"overview":"Opposites attract when, during their college days, Katie Morosky, a politically active Jew, meets Hubbell Gardiner, a feckless WASP. Years later, in the wake of World War II, they meet once again and, despite their obvious differences, attempt to make their love for each other work.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.522,"vote_count":503,"poster_path":"/o5x563ze56iI4iNsCBxTnDkt28i.jpg","release_date":"1973-10-17","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7mRpaVetpIde0f3Ebk2ipCAqDls.jpg","original_title":"The Way We Were","original_language":"en"},{"id":10239,"adult":false,"title":"A Tale of Autumn","video":false,"overview":"Magali, forty-something, is a winemaker and a widow: she loves her work but feels lonely. Her friends Rosine  and Isabelle both want secretly to find a husband for Magali.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.4861,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/1DQYFB5DENLWKUYdz5ttaVbDYnk.jpg","release_date":"1998-09-07","vote_average":7.082,"backdrop_path":"/jrbW0IOu7x24qFBSsAakgWOd9c9.jpg","original_title":"Conte d'automne","original_language":"fr"},{"id":661925,"adult":false,"title":"Softie","video":false,"overview":"Ten-year-old Johnny stands out from his family and his tough neighborhood in Eastern France. He's sensitive, intelligent and interested in all kinds of things way beyond his years. With