mer champion broncobuster and a young hitchhiker develop a special friendship.","genre_ids":[10770,35,18],"popularity":0.4407,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/6nKYyYLCOuevi8vlSocKZKPPCVr.jpg","release_date":"1996-01-01","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/aW7e9W8GIHK48RxMIhmn7OM5dzg.jpg","original_title":"Ruby Jean and Joe","original_language":"en"},{"id":10373,"adult":false,"title":"Quadrophenia","video":false,"overview":"Based on the 1973 rock opera album of the same name by The Who, this is the story of 60s teenager Jimmy. At work he slaves in a dead-end job. While after, he shops for tailored suits and rides his scooter as part of the London Mod scene.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":1.3626,"vote_count":279,"poster_path":"/4sRR3pvrAZMG7GEvnR9XzqyHHfD.jpg","release_date":"1979-09-14","vote_average":7.02,"backdrop_path":"/n31i51vwTOOUxKd1DWU2r6if0XR.jpg","original_title":"Quadrophenia","original_language":"en"},{"id":470551,"adult":false,"title":"Jembatan Pensil","video":false,"overview":"Inal, Nia, Aska, Yanti, Attar, and Ondeng struggled to get education in a free school built by the teacher. Inal, who is blind and Ondeng, who has “backwardness”, have to go through winding journeys to and from school. Ondeng's ability to draw sketches makes him always \"record\" everything he is passionate about: his father's life as a fisherman and the fragile bridge that his friends always walk on. His goal: to build the bridge. When that fragile bridge collapsed while they were crossing, it didn't discourage them. Ondeng's thoughts that always remember his father and his fear of being abandoned by his father made Ondeng out of control and did not realize the dangers of taking his own boat to the sea.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2264,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/8PTICCHLaU2Acboj9WPb92OgR2M.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-07","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Jembatan Pensil","original_language":"id"},{"id":10386,"adult":false,"title":"The Iron Giant","video":false,"overview":"In the small town of Rockwell, Maine in October 1957, a giant metal machine befriends a nine-year-old boy and ultimately finds its humanity by unselfishly saving people from their own fears and prejudices.","genre_ids":[16,878,10751,18],"popularity":6.5243,"vote_count":6041,"poster_path":"/ct04FCFLPImNG5thcPLRnVsZlmS.jpg","release_date":"1999-08-06","vote_average":7.949,"backdrop_path":"/wfClZdRb1x4LZ8B73Y9RSn8XAPa.jpg","original_title":"The Iron Giant","original_language":"en"},{"id":470317,"adult":false,"title":"Parava","video":false,"overview":"Irshad and Haseeb, two teenage boys from Mattanchery, share a passion for pigeon flying, a local game. Later, Irshad opens up about a tragic incident that ruined many friendships in the neighbourhood.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5521,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/2L6SAHw8VHEP18ePIK7L8ysAb7T.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-21","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/106oOZJ3LyqN4Qn6A1qW8eaFZMJ.jpg","original_title":"പറവ","original_language":"ml"},{"id":10464,"adult":false,"title":"Corrina, Corrina","video":false,"overview":"When Manny Singer's wife dies, his young daughter Molly becomes mute and withdrawn. To help cope with looking after Molly, he hires sassy housekeeper Corrina Washington, who coaxes Molly out of her shell and shows father and daughter a whole new way of life. Manny and Corrina's friendship delights Molly and enrages the other townspeople.","genre_ids":[35,10751,10749],"popularity":1.4488,"vote_count":446,"poster_path":"/xuEubxRGut2Yh118RyNa6ruXXCp.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-12","vote_average":6.689,"backdrop_path":"/uFh5qOyctqOOuEayOOoukE8CkV9.jpg","original_title":"Corrina, Corrina","original_language":"en"},{"id":662237,"adult":false,"title":"Sweet & Sour","video":false,"overview":"Faced with real-world opportunities and challenges, a couple endures the highs and lows of trying to make a long-distance relationship survive.","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"popularity":2.8474,"vo