od is a former teacher who lives as a recluse on the edge of town after his face is disfigured from an automobile accident ten years earlier, in which a boy was incinerated--and for which he was convicted of involuntary manslaughter. Also suspected of being a paedophile, he is befriended by Chuck, causing the town's suspicions and hostility to be ignited.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.3017,"vote_count":547,"poster_path":"/9dmH2jc6jwlZo90JQTFOx4XaBWt.jpg","release_date":"1993-08-25","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/eq5mrlYcu142Z8io1bdVPwGxx34.jpg","original_title":"The Man Without a Face","original_language":"en"},{"id":10510,"adult":false,"title":"Miracle on 34th Street","video":false,"overview":"Six-year-old Susan Walker has doubts about childhood's most enduring miracle—Santa Claus. Her mother told her the secret about Santa a long time ago, but, after meeting a special department store Santa who's convinced he's the real thing, Susan is given the most precious gift of all—something to believe in.","genre_ids":[14,18,10751],"popularity":3.6763,"vote_count":1131,"poster_path":"/iUTPKkljdEjPlcPPYgbUz7APnHu.jpg","release_date":"1994-11-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/oU0lGpUukjNOgZeuIqueNM3QiBE.jpg","original_title":"Miracle on 34th Street","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt15340724","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q110625579","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"365244","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/20th_century_girl"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":102947,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix ","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2022-10-21T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"12"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"","